caption_original: Dandelions. You have them. We have them. Want to get rid of them? Of course you do. Luckily, our scientists Dr. Russell Hynes and Dr. Karen Bailey have developed a new nature-based method that doesn’t require hours upon hours of weeding. Meet the Phoma macrostoma- a fungus that our team successfully isolated and is using to control unwanted dandelions! ow.ly/nohh30c80dF
